<text><body>
<pb ed="D" id="D06.8775.0001a" n="0001a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a01"/><milestone unit="juan" n="1"/><mulu type="卷" n="1"/><div1 type="other"><mulu type="其他" level="1" label="偈讚"/><lg id="lgD06p0001a0101" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em"><app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">稽首禮諸</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">&unrec;&unrec;&unrec;&unrec;</rdg></app>佛</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">及法比丘僧</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">今演毗&CB00112;法</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">令正法久住</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">戒如海無涯</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">如寶求無猒</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a02"/><l rend="text-indent:1em"><app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">欲護聖法財</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">&unrec;&unrec;&unrec;&unrec;&unrec;</rdg></app></l><l rend="text-indent:1em">眾集聽我&CB22072;</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">欲除四&CB00020;法</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">及滅僧殘法</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">障三十&CB22057;&CB18944;</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">眾集&CB10881;我&CB22072;</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a03"/><l rend="text-indent:1em"><app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">毗婆尸式&CB00020;</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">&unrec;&unrec;&unrec;&unrec;&unrec;</rdg></app></l><l rend="text-indent:1em">毗&CB22064;   &CB00236;&CB22627;孫</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">拘&CB06363;含牟&CB00112;</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">伽葉釋迦文</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">諸世尊大&CB18786;</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">為我&CB22072;是事</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a04"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">我今欲善&CB22072;</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">諸賢咸共&CB10881;</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">辟如人毀&CB30133;</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">不堪有所<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">涉</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">沙</rdg></app></l><l rend="text-indent:1em">毀戒亦如是</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">不得生天人</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a05"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">欲得生天上</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">為生人間者</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">常當護戒&CB30133;</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">勿令有毀損</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">如御入險道</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">失&CB00429;折軸憂</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a06"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">護戒亦如是</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">死時懷&CB06960;懼</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">如人自照鏡</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">好醜生欣慼</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">&CB22072;戒亦如是</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">全毀生憂喜</l>
<pb ed="D" id="D06.8775.0002a" n="0002a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a01"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">如兩陣共戰</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">勇怯有進退</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">&CB22072;戒亦如是</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">淨穢生安畏</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">世間王為最</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">眾流海為最</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a02"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">眾星月為最</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">眾聖佛為最</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">一切眾律中</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">戒經為上最</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">如來立禁戒</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">半月半月&CB22072;</l></lg></div1>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a03"/><div1 type="other"><mulu type="其他" level="1" label="六法文"/><p id="pD06p0002a0301">&unrec;&unrec;六法文<note place="inline">佛言&unrec;&unrec;&unrec;入眾&unrec;&CB22072;六名字</note>某甲聽如來無所&CB00473;<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">等</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">&unrec;</rdg></app>正覺&CB22072;六法。</p><list><item id="itemD06p0002a0332"><p id="pD06p0002a0332" place="inline">不得犯不淨行
<lb ed="D" n="0002a04"/>行&CB21942;欲法若式&CB01415;摩&CB06363;行&CB21942;欲法非式&CB01415;摩&CB06363;非釋種女若与染汙心男
<lb ed="D" n="0002a05"/>子身相觸&CB04130;戒應更与戒是中盡形壽不得犯能持不<note place="inline">荅言能持</note>。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0002a0526"><p id="pD06p0002a0526" place="inline">不淂偷盜乃至
<lb ed="D" n="0002a06"/>草&CB01007;為式&CB01415;摩&CB06363;取人五錢若自取教人取若<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">自</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">&lac;</rdg></app>斫教人斫若燒若壞
<lb ed="D" n="0002a07"/>色非式&CB01415;摩&CB06363;非釋種女若取減五錢&CB04130;戒應更与戒是中盡形壽不淂
<lb ed="D" n="0002a08"/>犯能持不<note place="inline">荅言能持</note>。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0002a0809"><p id="pD06p0002a0809" place="inline">不淂故&CB07589;眾生命乃至蟻子若&CB01415;式摩&CB06363;故自手&CB07589;人
<lb ed="D" n="0002a09"/>命求刀与人教死讚死若与非藥若&CB18919;胎若猒禱&CB00057;術自作教人作者非<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">式&CB01415;</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">&CB01415;式</rdg></app>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a10"/>摩&CB06363;非釋種女若&CB07589;畜生不能變<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">化</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">作</rdg></app>者命&CB04130;戒應更与戒是中盡形壽不
<lb ed="D" n="0002a11"/>淂犯能持不<note place="inline">荅言能持</note>。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0002a1110"><p id="pD06p0002a1110" place="inline">不淂妄語乃至戲<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">笑</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">&unrec;</rdg></app>若&CB01415;式摩&CB06363;不真實非<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">己</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">巳</rdg></app>有自稱
<lb ed="D" n="0002a12"/>言淂上人法淂解脫三昧正授淂&CB00824;&CB00442;琲G斯&CB00442;含果阿&CB06363;含果阿羅漢果天
<lb ed="D" n="0002a13"/>來龍來鬼來供養我此非式&CB01415;摩&CB06363;非釋種女若於眾中故作妄語&CB04130;戒
<lb ed="D" n="0002a14"/>應更与戒是中盡形壽不淂犯能持不<note place="inline">荅言能持</note>。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0002a1420"><p id="pD06p0002a1420" place="inline">不淂非時食若式&CB01415;摩&CB06363;非時
<lb ed="D" n="0002a15"/>食&CB04130;戒應更与戒是中盡形壽不淂犯能持不<note place="inline">荅言能持</note>。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0002a1523"><p id="pD06p0002a1523" place="inline">不淂飲酒若式&CB01415;摩&CB06363;
<lb ed="D" n="0002a16"/>飲酒&CB04130;戒應更与戒是中盡形壽不淂犯能持不<note place="inline">荅言能持</note>。</p></item></list></div1><div1 type="other"><mulu type="其他" level="1" label="具學三法"/><p id="pD06p0002a1624" place="inline">佛言式&CB01415;摩&CB06363;一切大&CB00112;
<lb ed="D" n="0002a17"/>戒應學除自手受食与他此學法女具學三法。</p><list><item id="itemD06p0002a1719"><p id="pD06p0002a1719" place="inline">一學根本法即四重是。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0002a1728"><p id="pD06p0002a1728" place="inline">二學六
<lb ed="D" n="0002a18"/>法<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">謂</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">為</rdg></app>染汙心相觸盜五錢&CB07589;眾生命小妄語非時食飲酒。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0002a1823"><p id="pD06p0002a1823" place="inline">三學行法謂大&CB00112;<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">諸</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">&unrec;</rdg></app>戒
<pb ed="D" id="D06.8775.0003a" n="0003a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a01"/>及威儀並制學之若犯根本應滅&CB11462;若&CB04130;學法者更与二年羯磨若違行法
<lb ed="D" n="0003a02"/>直犯佛教即&CB00824;懺悔不壞本所學六法。</p></item></list></div1><div1 type="other"><mulu type="其他" level="1" label="應學十八法"/><p id="pD06p0003a0216" place="inline">僧祇律<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">第</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">&unrec;</rdg></app>卅卷云式&CB01415;&CB00112;應學十八法
<lb ed="D" n="0003a03"/>若式&CB01415;摩&CB06363;&CB00112;不學十八法非式&CB01415;&CB00112;何&CB21717;十八。</p><list><item id="itemD06p0003a0320"><p id="pD06p0003a0320" place="inline">一一切比丘&CB00112;下。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0003a0327"><p id="pD06p0003a0327" place="inline">二一切沙&CB12752;&CB00112;上。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0003a0334"><p id="pD06p0003a0334" place="inline">三於式
<lb ed="D" n="0003a04"/>&CB01415;摩&CB06363;&CB00112;不淨於大&CB00112;淨。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0003a0411"><p id="pD06p0003a0411" place="inline">四於大不淨式&CB01415;&CB00112;亦不淨。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0003a0422"><p id="pD06p0003a0422" place="inline">五大&CB00112;淂与式&CB01415;三宿。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0003a0431"><p id="pD06p0003a0431" place="inline">六
<lb ed="D" n="0003a05"/>式&CB01415;&CB00112;淂与沙&CB12752;&CB00112;三宿。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0003a0511"><p id="pD06p0003a0511" place="inline">七式&CB01415;&CB00112;淂与大&CB00112;授食。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0003a0521"><p id="pD06p0003a0521" place="inline">八除火淨五生種取金銀及
<lb ed="D" n="0003a06"/>錢。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0003a0602"><p id="pD06p0003a0602" place="inline">九自&CB30130;沙&CB12752;授食。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0003a0609"><p id="pD06p0003a0609" place="inline">十&CB00112;不淂向&CB22072;七聚名淂不煞不盜不&CB21942;不妄語如
<lb ed="D" n="0003a07"/>是&CB21717;。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0003a0703"><p id="pD06p0003a0703" place="inline">十一式&CB01415;&CB00112;至布&CB16765;自恣日入僧中&CI0004;合掌作如是言阿闍梨耶
<lb ed="D" n="0003a08"/>僧我某甲清淨憶念持如是三&CB22072;而去。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0003a0816"><p id="pD06p0003a0816" place="inline">十二後四波羅夷犯者始學。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0003a0827"><p id="pD06p0003a0827" place="inline">十三十九
<lb ed="D" n="0003a09"/>僧伽婆尸沙<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">巳</rdg></app>下一一犯&CB18919;所作突吉羅。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0003a0917"><p id="pD06p0003a0917" place="inline">十四若破五戒&CB18919;犯日數更學何&CB21717;五非時食。</p></item>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a10"/><item id="itemD06p0003a1001"><p id="pD06p0003a1001">十五停食〃犯吉羅停食〃者謂旦起受食<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">至中</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">&unrec;</rdg></app>過中<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">巳</rdg></app>去限一&CB00824;臾若過二時
<lb ed="D" n="0003a11"/>名曰非時也式&CB01415;&CB00112;晨起應淨洗手齊腕以前不淂粗魯洗五指頭當以&CB01926;土
<lb ed="D" n="0003a12"/>揩洗令作聲洗更相摩者不淨更&CB00824;洗之。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0003a1217"><p id="pD06p0003a1217" place="inline">十六捉錢金銀。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0003a1223"><p id="pD06p0003a1223" place="inline">十七飲酒。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0003a1227"><p id="pD06p0003a1227" place="inline">十八著
<lb ed="D" n="0003a13"/>花者。</p></item></list>是名十八&unrec;。<p id="pD06p0003a1308" place="inline">是式&CB01415;摩&CB06363;二&CB15329;學戒法。十誦律云為度任身女後<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">起</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">超</rdg></app>過佛
<lb ed="D" n="0003a14"/><app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">令</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">今</rdg></app>二&CB15329;學之可知若式&CB01415;&CB00112;行法式&CB01415;&CB00112;不淂与大&CB00112;為伴<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">巳</rdg></app>戒不滿故自不淂与沙&CB12752;
<lb ed="D" n="0003a15"/>&CB00112;為伴以非同學故若二&CB00112;兼一式&CB01415;&CB00112;若二式&CB01415;&CB00112;兼一沙&CB12752;&CB00112;為伴餘人不合也。</p></div1>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a16"/><div1 type="other"><mulu type="其他" level="1" label="十戒相"/><head>十戒相</head><p id="pD06p0003a1604" place="inline"><note place="inline">沙&CB12752;者此云息&CB08891;行慈故曰沙&CB12752;息於十惡故受十戒<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">耳</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">取</rdg></app>慈念眾生故有不<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">煞</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">&unrec;</rdg></app>&CB21717;也此之十戒乃至眾戒根本先護持之也</note>。</p><list><item id="itemD06p0003a1651"><p id="pD06p0003a1651" place="inline">一不煞若故煞人不淂受大戒
<lb ed="D" n="0003a17"/>若煞畜生&CB21717;至心懺悔淂滅。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0003a1712"><p id="pD06p0003a1712" place="inline">二不盜若偷若&CB04068;若<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">強奪</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">&unrec;&unrec;</rdg></app>若燒若&CB02167;<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">壞</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">懷</rdg></app>他物但直五錢
<lb ed="D" n="0003a18"/><app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">与</rdg></app>上不淂受大戒若<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">減五</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">五減</rdg></app>錢若非人畜生物懺悔淂滅。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0003a1822"><p id="pD06p0003a1822" place="inline">三不&CB21942;若人男女若非人男女若
<pb ed="D" id="D06.8775.0004a" n="0004a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a01"/>畜生男女若侵身分不得大戒若摩觸&CB21717;至心懺悔淂滅。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0004a0123"><p id="pD06p0004a0123" place="inline">四不妄語若稱淂聖不
<lb ed="D" n="0004a02"/>淂受大戒若以重事謗清淨人及誑或欺妄其罪難懺悔餘小妄語&CB17714;懺悔<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">巳</rdg></app>進大
<lb ed="D" n="0004a03"/>戒。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0004a0302"><p id="pD06p0004a0302" place="inline">五不飲酒<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">酒</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">&lac;</rdg></app>性能發人煩&CB08974;改人心性&CB07455;人道心多<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">開</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">聞</rdg></app>眾過之門若酒入腹護戒心&CB02812;自
<lb ed="D" n="0004a04"/>制不能淂故宜深防不服狂藥也。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0004a0414"><p id="pD06p0004a0414" place="inline">六不淂&CB00473;花   &CB13059;香油塗身莊&CB00496;花&CB00672;<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">愛翫</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">受習</rdg></app>其身
<lb ed="D" n="0004a05"/>內懷深&CB00473;情惑&CB07455;道。</p></item><item id="itemD06p0004a0509"><p id="pD06p0004a0509" place="inline">七不歌&CB01425;唱妓及往觀&CB17714;習近喜&CB00554;放縱身口外恣蕩逸道心
