<lb ed="D" n="0005a11"/>某甲律師<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">巳</rdg></app>有妹為某甲律師故善護持&CB00473;用&CB18919;&CB10318;緣。</p></div1>
